snippet.title: Kairo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Kairo the new game by Locked Door Puzzle is an atmospheric puzzle solving adventure game set in a minimalist abstract world.

Available from http://kairo.lockeddoorpuzzle.com

game by Richard Perrin
music by Wounds
